"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Wanna help out a small fish and/or a friend you recently onboarded to PoolTogether v4? Great news: you can delegate your winning chances over to them with just a few clicks\\n\\nThe feature isnâ€™t available on the PoolTogether v4 UI just yet, so youâ€™ll have to do it from the smart contract\\n\\n**\\\\*\\\\*\\\\*We will be doing this from polygonscan, so make sure your funds (and the accountâ€™s funds youâ€™re delegating to) have been deposited to the Polygon network\\\\*\\\\*\\\\***\\n\\nHereâ€™s how you do it:\\n\\nStep one: go to the [PTaUSDC contract](https://polygonscan.com/address/0x6a304dFdb9f808741244b6bfEe65ca7B3b3A6076#writeContract) on polygonscan\\n\\nStep two: scroll down to the verified contract, click on the **Write Contract** button (or **Write** button if on mobile), and connect using Metamask or WalletConnect\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Kr0gOSg5V4li2bBl3WEoi.jpeg?height=2000&width=1125)\\n\\nStep three: once connected scroll down to number 7, the **delegate** function\\n\\nStep four: enter the address you wish to delegate to and click **Write**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/MxtODvA8nMCEjU1t6BbtW.jpeg?height=2000&width=1125)\\n\\nStep five: pay the gas fee\\n\\nAnd youâ€™re done!\\n\\nWhen you go back to your PoolTogether account page, you will see that your daily and weekly odds are now both zero. You can also get confirmation of your delegation from the contact by switching from **Write Contract** to **Read Contract** and scrolling down to function number 6, **delegateOf**. There you will input your own wallet address and then hit **Query**. It will return the address you are currently delegating to\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/scZ_gSMDEZd2RgGc9nmyK.jpeg?height=2000&width=1125)\\n\\nIf you would like to take back your delegation and recover your winning chances for yourself, simply follow the steps again and this time input your own address into the **delegate** function. EZPZ ðŸ˜Ž have fun!\",\"timestamp\":1641637755,\"title\":\"How to delegate your winning chances to others on PoolTogether v4\"},\"digest\":\"runk-Y-j2t7ZokA1eWoyEj4X2LYAIWbzjlsDnLiMU4s\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x86aa399A62b6D89f4d6306c82656bE29CB2E728A\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"qcsq99m5VKQk83DbyknPqJO3Zo3mWpcTRzxFwa1pWNc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"u5Zid0SjOCmE7vDivuQPBIsd81ZHeAnMh89J9KfbhR4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"lK90cCyboOFzEDVVUrfTsbOi3rtamHI0_sY8ARLnuwZV-iZ8ehrjF7hC1laTAQBWZM_gVHOi2k3rpgJotIdTgQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xbf608bd6115cc71f6809d74bd257e784b790ec8a00020706c78652d98a61e12174224d91d64ae8124a7cbe04e4c06dabd1e54469c5c14c99157fecd036a913951c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"qcsq99m5VKQk83DbyknPqJO3Zo3mWpcTRzxFwa1pWNc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"u5Zid0SjOCmE7vDivuQPBIsd81ZHeAnMh89J9KfbhR4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"runk-Y-j2t7ZokA1eWoyEj4X2LYAIWbzjlsDnLiMU4s\"}"